	(text "IM73A135 VDD is 2.75 V MICBIAS; C40 and C44 are the per-microphone 100 nF bypass capacitors \nand C41 is the shared 1 uF MICBIAS capacitor.\nMK1 drives ADC IN1P/IN1M and MK2 drives ADC IN2P/IN2M; keep both differential pairs matched. \nMK2 is populated for R0 and may become DNP after validation.\nEnclosure: use a sealed external acoustic chimney, isolated from the BMP581 ePTFE atmospheric vent."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 235.458 229.108 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.016 1.016)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "ae52dc96-869e-485a-927f-286f7fc5f8ad")
	)
	(text "BQ25611D NVDC: hardware CE keeps charging disabled through reset. Firmware writes charge/OTG disabled first; \n960 mA is the register step for the 1.0 A normal R0 policy; 1500 mA only after thermal validation. \nOTG remains disabled and charger D+/D- are test pads only.\nSamsung INR18650-35E reference cell: factory-welded tabs to plated PCB slots; cradle carries all mechanical load."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 16.764 156.718 0)
		(effects
